Package: TreeArchi
Title: Tools for Exploring Size-Independent and Nonlinear Tree Architecture
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Elisa", "Sillfors", email = "elisa.sillfors@helsinki.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for analysing tree architectural traits through size-controlled 
    models that capture nonlinear and interaction-dependent relationships among 
    traits. The package is designed to identify architectural coordination and 
    network structure beyond simple allometric scaling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
